Files under `src/vendor/` are derived from KeyPeek's `src/layout_key.rs` and
`src/qmk_keycode_labels/` (the QMK/VIA keycode-label tables). They are reused and
reshaped for Keyplane under the terms of the GPL-3.0. Modifications from upstream
are noted in `src/vendor/mod.rs`:

  - module paths rehomed under `crate::vendor::*`;
  - modifier symbols use plain text instead of egui icon-font glyphs (dropping
    the egui/eframe UI dependency, since Keyplane renders in a web frontend).

